title: How to Deal with Disappointments in Life
description: In this episode, we talk about how to not only deal with disappoints, but as well as trusting God's journey for you.Do not forget that if you would like, you can make a donation to support this podcast, and you can also leave us voice messages through Anchor! --- Send in a voice message: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/message Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/support
